/**
   * PAN card format validation
   * Pattern: 5 alphabets + 4 digits + 1 alphabet (case-insensitive)
   * Example: ABCDE1234F
   */
⋮----
/**
   * Indian Mobile number format validation
   * Pattern: Exactly 10 digits starting with 6-9 (India specific)
   * Example: 9876543210, 8123456789
   */
⋮----
/**
   * Pincode format validation
   * Pattern: Exactly 6 digits
   * Example: 400001
   */
⋮----
/**
   * Salary date validation (1-31)
   * Pattern: Accepts 1-31 with or without leading zero
   * Examples: 1, 01, 15, 31
   */
⋮----
/**
   * Monthly income validation (1000 to 10,00,000)
   * Pattern: Allows numbers from 1000 to 1000000 with optional decimal places up to 2 digits
   * Examples: 1000, 15000, 500000, 1000000, 25000.50
   */
